title: Virgin Galactic delays introduction of second suborbital spaceship
summary: Virgin Galactic’s second suborbital spaceplane won’t enter service in 2023 as previously planned because of demands on company personnel to both return the first spaceplane to flight and begin work on a next generation of vehicles.

title: Long March 5B rocket reenters over Pacific Ocean after forcing airspace closures in Europe
summary: A large rocket stage used to launch the final module for China’s space station made an uncontrolled reentry into the atmosphere Friday after precautionary airspace closures took effect in southern Europe.

title: SpaceX launches Hotbird 13G to extend Eutelsat’s broadcast coverage
summary: SpaceX launched the second of two satellites for Eutelsat Nov. 3 to replenish one of the largest broadcast systems in Europe, the Middle East and Northern Africa.

title: NRO to sign deals with commercial providers of hyperspectral imaging
summary: The NRO plans to soon release a request for proposals for commercial hyperspectral satellite data
